libapache-voodoo-perl (3.0200-1) lucid; urgency=low

  * Added dependance on Data::Structure::Util
  * Moved all the cleanup tasks to an Apache cleanup handler, thus making
    the system more responsive.
  * Fixed a glitch in Debug/Log4perl.pm.  The Apache.Voodoo name space works
    again.
  * Cleaned up the debug javascript to remove inadvertent use of reserved
    keywords, and to to be more jslint compliant.

 -- Maverick Edwards <maverick@smurfbane.org>  Tue, 1 June 2010 15:17:44 -0500

libapache-voodoo-perl (3.0102-1) lucid; urgency=low

  * Removed dependance on IPC::SharedCache
  * Fixed the tardis()
  * Minor refactor of try/catch block for calling a controller so that
    it could retain profiling information.

 -- Maverick Edwards <maverick@smurfbane.org>  Tue, 1 June 2010 15:17:44 -0500

